{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"3212767a33","title":"对身后的预言","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"ad6cafea58","index":0,"year":1939,"month":null,"day":null,"articleId":"3212767a33"}],"tags":[{"id":"29143cbd32","name":"无产阶级国际主义","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","name":"斯大林选集（诸夏怀斯社2017年5月）","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"斯大林，诸夏怀斯社2017年5月","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives5/main/d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"1332d101b8","name":"斯大林"}]},"publication_details":{"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"4eafaf554e","type":"paragraph","text":"对身后的预言","index":0,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3212767a33"},{"id":"f49bae9016","type":"paragraph","text":"（1939年）","index":1,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3212767a33"},{"id":"92f94d26c0","type":"paragraph","text":"斯大林不仅是一位伟大的战略家，而且是一位伟大的预言家。1939年，即在我国后来发生的事件之前半个世纪，他就预言（女革命家亚·米·柯伦泰记下了他的话）：","index":2,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3212767a33"},{"id":"c2d5349017","type":"paragraph","text":"我们党和人民的许多事情会遭到金曲和迹茂，首先是在国外，国内也一样。","index":3,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3212767a33"},{"id":"5d1403e497","type":"paragraph","text":"追求世界统治地位的犹太复国主义将因为我们的成就而报复我们它依旧把俄罗斯看成是一个野蛋国家和供应原料的附属国。我的名字也将遭到党骂和训榜，许多暴行会都会强加于我。","index":4,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3212767a33"},{"id":"7736e6137d","type":"paragraph","text":"世界犹太复国主义将尽全力来推毁我们的联盟，使俄罗斯再也不能站立起来。","index":5,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3212767a33"},{"id":"522e0e8ded","type":"paragraph","text":"苏联的力量在于各族人民友好。故人攻击的矛头应当首先指向破环这种友谊，指向使周边地区脱离俄罗斯的企图。在这方面，应当承认，我们做得还不是尽善尽美。","index":6,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3212767a33"},{"id":"7b3e9a7115","type":"paragraph","text":"民族主义将特别严重地兴起。在一定时期内，它将压倒国际主义和爱国主义，不过时间不长。各个民族内部都会出现许多狼项的领袖和叛徒。","index":7,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3212767a33"},{"id":"cdbc1049d5","type":"paragraph","text":"整个说来，未来的发展道路将更加复杂，甚至疯狂，转折将是最急剧的。结局将是东方翻腾起来，同时西方也会出现尖锐的矛盾。","index":8,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3212767a33"},{"id":"125a964003","type":"paragraph","text":"不论事态如何发展，一段时间之后，子孙后代的日光仍将关注着我们社会主义祖国的活动和胜利。后代人将举起自己先辈的旗帜，他们将按照自己过去的榜样来建设自己的未来引自《大元帅斯大林》","index":9,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3212767a33"},{"id":"acce0a85e3","type":"paragraph","text":"选自新编《斯大林全集","index":10,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3212767a33"},{"id":"79d39eff0f","type":"paragraph","text":"档案附卷一第220—221页2005年版第795-796页","index":11,"publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3212767a33"}],"page":{"id":"323b5619f3","publicationId":"d4ea93d0-aee6-435e-bd9c-5020dfb6fc0d","articleId":"3212767a33","start":2514,"end":2515}}}},"__N_SSG":true}